    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced chicken</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and the <strong>juice</strong> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong> lemon</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1580805803906-x200.jpg",
