    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Slice the<strong> remaining 1/2</strong> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> wedges</p><p>Finely chop the <strong>parsley</strong> (including the stalks)</p>",
