    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, add the <strong>clotted cream</strong>, <strong>peas</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong> and cook for 1 min or until everything is warmed through</p><p>Add the<strong> drained spaghetti</strong> and <strong>chopped parsley</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>lemony chicken & pea spaghetti</strong></p>",
